    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Servicing Greater Geelong, Melbourne &amp; Regional Victoria</p>
      <h1>Making Solar &amp; Batteries<br class="hero-br"> Reliable for Years to Come</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Honest advice, quality workmanship and long-term support from our local team in Geelong and Torquay.<br class="subtitle-br"> Trusted by thousands of Victorian homes and businesses to deliver real savings.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#solar-qualifier" class="btn btn-primary"><svg class="btn-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="m19 12-7 7-7-7"/></svg>Get Your Free Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bottom-bar">
      <div class="hero-pills-row">
        <div class="hero-pill">
          <svg class="pill-check" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M5 10l3.5 3.5L15 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Solar Victoria Accredited</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-pill">
          <svg class="pill-check" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M5 10l3.5 3.5L15 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
