            <div class="service-card-content">
              <h3>Residential Systems</h3>
              <p>Power your home with clean, affordable energy and enjoy long-term savings with our tailored residential solar systems.</p>
              <a href="/services/residential" class="service-card-btn">See Examples</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card" style="background-image: url('/image/photography/comerical_V1.webp');">
