          <div class="guarantee-text">
            <h3>Ongoing support</h3>
            <p>We monitor your system after install and are a phone call away if anything needs attention.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="guarantee-card">
          <div class="guarantee-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="8" y="10" rx="3" width="14" height="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <rect x="18" y="18" rx="3" width="14" height="12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              <path d="M12 16h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M22 24h6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M12 34l2-4 2 2 3-6 2 3 3-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="guarantee-text">
            <h3>Straight-up quotes</h3>
            <p>All performance estimates are completed using accurate data and conservative when it comes to cost.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="guarantee-card">
          <div class="guarantee-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M20 10l-10 6v8c0 5 4 9.5 10 12 6-2.5 10-7 10-12v-8l-10-6z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M16 22l3 3 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="guarantee-text">
            <h3>Backed by warranties</h3>
