          <div class="step-marker">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <div class="step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Free remote consultation</h3>
            <p>We'll put together a tailored design with upfront costs and realistic savings estimates. Our solar team will give you a call to walk through everything — no obligation, no pressure.</p>
